import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ServiceService } from '../../Service/service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-get-all-data', templateUrl: './get-all-data.component.html', styleUrls: ['./get-all-data.component.css'] }) export class GetAllDataComponent { result: any; constructor( private service: ServiceService ){ } onSubmit():void{ this.service.getAllData().subscribe((data: any) => { console.log(data); this.result=data; console.log(this.result); return this.result }) } }
